## ✔️ Circuit Breaker

You can opt in to a per-origin circuit breaker that prevents repeated calls to an unhealthy origin while still allowing recovery through deterministic half-open probes.

Set `circuitBreaker: true` to enable it with the defaults, or pass an object to customize it:

```ts
await ofetch("https://api.example.com/data", {
